This directory contains the software ArbAlign, published in the work referenced
in the file original_ref.bib. Two python files are included:

 - ArbAlign.py: contains the main call to ArbAlign algorithm.

 - ArbAlign-driver.py: contains the driver to the main call.

 - PrinCoords.py: is a procedure to rotate a structure into its principal axes
                  of inertia. This is a precondition to ArbAlign.



There has been a modification done. In detail:

 - PrinCoords.py:
     A mistake for the element CU at line number 69 was corrected. Originally: CO.
